cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper deals with deep learning models and their calibration, which are topics that are commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper specifically focuses on deep learning models and their calibration, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.NE.
